            <h4 class="font-headline text-lg font-bold uppercase mb-2 group-hover:text-[#00eefc]">Narrative Experiment: Ren'py</h4>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-[#ababab] leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-grow font-light">
              Exploring branching narratives and choice-driven storytelling through visual novel engines.
            </p>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mt-auto pt-4 border-t border-white/5">
              <span class="text-[9px] font-bold text-[#00eefc] uppercase tracking-widest">Ren'py / Python</span>
              <a href="/game-demo" target="_blank" class="text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-white hover:text-[#e4f700] transition-colors">
                Play Demo
